 se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b46b96e7-4b57-406e-9a24-e42d62fd1c95\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>도무송 칼선 모양</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5244954f-ee19-4439-a107-4efba656c6a7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-18784d71-797b-466d-92a5-c98b11c5ce90\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">디자인에 반영되는 톰슨(도무송)칼선의 모양은 다음과 같이 이루어져 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4885c672-d450-4638-b718-8c42f53d28c2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4885c672-d450-4638-b718-8c42f53d28c2\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTRfMTQ3/MDAxNjY1NzMxNzc2MDYz.qYXGdU8riYhzPq97XamHznqbWRiHVkjQxyrdDLQVAmEg.tIppc_aB_GXWppTi2f-sSD4dbFMpAw73klLVWUdWpOsg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2009\", \"originalHeight\" : \"828\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTRfMTQ3/MDAxNjY1NzMxNzc2MDYz.qYXGdU8riYhzPq97XamHznqbWRiHVkjQxyrdDLQVAmEg.tIppc_aB_GXWppTi2f-sSD4dbFMpAw73klLVWUdWpOsg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0aeb92ec-ef50-4802-a289-e36868f05c50\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-81e6f8b3-33bd-439d-be99-ae3002e13e5a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-da47f317-08c8-49e6-9e38-ef02bdd1a3a1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a6b01b0d-27d3-4513-8d28-815d7f84a814\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c8cf2df5-c688-4e78-8d4d-3c40ecde5af8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">쇼핑백의 칼선은 추후 나중에 자세하게 다루겠습니다. 이번에 하나만 말씀드리면 측면에 위아래 디자인 사항과 상단, 하단 접착부분에는 가급적 인쇄잉크를 묻히지 않고 접착할 수 있도록 작업을 하게됩니다. 쇼핑백은 기본적으로 측면접착 그리고 하단에 접착을 기본으로 하며 상단은 접어서 하도메라는 종이를 대서 빳빳하게 만드는 작업을 합니다. 나중에 자세히 설명하도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-516da97c-ebf1-4f84-846e-3a9834a9a4bf\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9d7c172c-00fb-49ee-8863-39339a4ffc7f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-ea74a7f5-2ab5-43e4-9a75-3721c249d107\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f962431c-ee0a-4f47-97f6-494a56fb8a24\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-786c0e7c-561b-4ce3-9f62-0613fab2be0d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4ca9db32-adba-49e2-8717-145a7927da48\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70fc3257-beb8-4e33-a1bd-998f23614b38\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-864d1485-a6db-4c76-a0b8-d2d9b5091fc4\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">쇼핑백에 사용되는 용지는 일반적으로 통용되는 거의 모든 종이가 가능하며 찢어짐을 방지하기 위해 코팅처리를 하는것이 일반적입니다. 보통의 경우 물건을 이동하는 포장상품이기 때문에 무게에 찢어지거나 하는 부분이 민감할 수 있습니다. 코팅하는것을 추천드립니다. 종이는 108g 아트지나 스노우지가 일반적인 종이를 사용하고 코팅으로 종이를 보호합니다. 그 외에 랑데뷰나 반누브등 고급지를 사용하기도 하며 크라프트지나 독특한 종이에 로고의 박인쇄로만 처리하는 쇼핑백도 많습니다. 추후 샘플 사진과 함께 자세하게 다루는 시간이 있을겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bbee41c0-c85f-479e-b55f-005ec0c8387a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-17006c3d-a551-40aa-95ca-93b79d69627f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-af778178-0eeb-4d6d-8a4c-a48a38266e36\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-0c514fed-b982-4e78-b3a7-d3811680907c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-9c45080d-2daa-47e6-94db-dfeb671e2320\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-08f835d9-ac94-4f4f-b254-326c3c182a19\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eca655bf-4b91-44aa-a47a-4794d031c81f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e6b519b4-46a0-42fb-ae62-fe9eb3ac931e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>아일렛</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bb888999-75ae-407c-8212-9bdcc20a0033\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-71553603-df94-469d-bbd0-5858723ec770\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">아일렛은 추가 사항입니다. 일반적으로 작업되지만 없는 경우도 있습니다. 아일렛은 몇가지의 색을 선택할 수도 있습니다. 가장 흔한 색은 흰색 또는 검정색입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9cfa7e2e-123e-4338-9bcb-8062fc1bb3cb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-9cfa7e2e-123e-4338-9bcb-8062fc1bb3cb\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTRfMTUx/MDAxNjY1NzMyNzAzMTA3.wHN7ZuhbdHlveX1NyCCWLJOmIiNDA4hs0sfFIuNF1oog.4i49DKLJHCGfzjh8TPAGiBJ21tBQ-n3jLjkPosrJFwAg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"2068\", \"originalHeight\" : \"812\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTRfMTUx/MDAxNjY1NzMyNzAzMTA3.wHN7ZuhbdHlveX1NyCCWLJOmIiNDA4hs0sfFIuNF1oog.4i49DKLJHCGfzjh8TPAGiBJ21tBQ-n3jLjkPosrJFwAg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6fac2e39-9997-4512-8816-781ae8a22725\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3a0758ef-486c-4245-bc2d-5c640722e97e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8bee0284-6839-452a-ae02-eaf504418062\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1bbad8d9-b324-455c-90d9-4f14128f334a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-bd417493-18c5-4ee1-992b-d0a38e30ccfb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-5c668496-3505-4e87-b1ec-16659fbb7e9b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-42e50ab3-990a-4ff1-85e4-c42f06f6b777\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-957f4255-6bb9-4811-a594-734516227b03\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-99381e43-bafb-4e50-b4cf-d5906e6d500d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>끈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9892fdcf-0546-4887-8b8f-104aef5266ac\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2d93c0f6-3ed5-4488-907b-e222bcb21f7d\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">쇼핑백 끈은 여러가지 종류가 있습니다. 쇼핑백의 무게와 모양에 따라 바꿀 수 있으며 끈을 묶어서 마무리 할수 도 있고 철팁으로 마무리할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ff770fa0-cff9-4b87-9fa9-bb285a751bac\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ff770fa0-cff9-4b87-9fa9-bb285a751bac\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTRfMTQg/MDAxNjY1NzMzNDcyMjg1.F1A3KMpusyOJ2-m1wnhGp_BH4wCfXfO2n_CKRWLLHuYg.X2KkL3HVxRIycS_28cHdPfBiX6lcADpUDIQVzA286JMg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3105\", \"originalHeight\" : \"451\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTRfMTQg/MDAxNjY1NzMzNDcyMjg1.F1A3KMpusyOJ2-m1wnhGp_BH4wCfXfO2n_CKRWLLHuYg.X2KkL3HVxRIycS_28cHdPfBiX6lcADpUDIQVzA286JMg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d13fa018-909a-45bb-a478-8d01be99401a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d13fa018-909a-45bb-a478-8d01be99401a\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTRfMTg5/MDAxNjY1NzU1NjMyNzcy.XTukP8OFgZj_CRb0tDMKSoUk51ZElZl3aqtEox9_tUIg.a7Cc8eV9Am22dn-keiJ_nUM46NJ-MfSGvEzaibt_ArQg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3100\", \"originalHeight\" : \"497\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjEwMTRfMTg5/MDAxNjY1NzU1NjMyNzcy.XTukP8OFgZj_CRb0tDMKSoUk51ZElZl3aqtEox9_tUIg.a7Cc8eV9Am22dn-keiJ_nUM46NJ-MfSGvEzaibt_ArQg.PNG.cookthedesign/10%EC%9D%B8%EC%87%84_%ED%99%8D%EB%B3%B4_221013.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3b7185cf-5f18-4845-91f6-a054ffd0d3e3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3371997b-0c7a-430f-b863-b08c4c0e32a2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7f25b693-689c-4d02-930f-32b5d335a5f1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-f13103fd-f8f9-415d-8c93-1407c6084098\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a3c3d60b-db57-4842-b543-efbfa2349a4d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e61c3f3f-6bde-4f48-8721-53ec5cdc2071\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-805da111-4b1c-4134-bce4-06dfbd49c63c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>주의사항</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-98d645de-e4d6-4fa7-ba4c-1fd8ef4957f6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5d3186bf-ba83-405e-9d97-77e4e50dacfb\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\">쇼핑백은 대량을 제외하고는 대부분 수가공으로 접고 풀발이나 양면테이프 마감을 합니다. 주문 접수시 납기를 반드시 확인해야합니다. 기본 수량의 경우 대부분 10~15일 이상 소요됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-06f4a65c-423d-4b6f-8894-40bc483850ed\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-5b663557-d1f1-4e36-ba4a-e27d06eaec40\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2fbcd7ff-f21e-4d88-b1a6-fe0bdf61c243\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2902b6ed-2a1e-4aea-a900-76cd60b2e896\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-982246f6-6f7a-41c9-a88a-a6633b46df9b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6120ba20-9e59-419e-94a3-8e44741093f3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4730a8f2-69e0-49aa-bacf-07ce1fc703b0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니이 찾는 리퍼럴(referral)</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bb39dba1-07e2-4404-948d-62aa3fcefa1f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-left\" id=\"SE-a4aa1e88-4dec-477f-915b-744178aa95b1\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-sty